<h1>Welcome to Your Immersive Idea</h1>
<div>
    This is a tool to create immersive 3d diagrams and collaborate in real time with other users. It is in very early
    stages of development,
    but currently there is a public space where multiple users can gather and co-edit environments. Additionally there
    is a private area where you can
    experiment with the controls and learn...note the private area all diagrams are lost when you close your browser.
    <p>
        Currently this works best on oculus quest, though there is limited "view only" capability for desktop browsers
        and mobile phones.
    </p>
</div>
<div id="leftDiv">
    <ul id="mainmenu">
        <li><a href="/local">Local Playground</a>
            <p>Edit objects in a private space. Stored only in memory, not shared with anyone, will be erased when you
                close your browser. Only accessible on a single device.</p>
        </li>
        <li><a href="/login">Log In</a>
            <p>Log in or create a new account to use the multiuser collaborative experience</p></li>
        </li>
        <li><a href="/worlds/public">Public Playground</a>
            <p>Any authenticated user can create, edit, manipulate objects in this space.</p>
        </li>
        <li><a href="/home">Your Private Space</a>
            <p>Edit objects in a private space.  Stored in cloud database, only accessible to you.  Only accessible if you log in.</p>
        </li>
    </ul>
</div>
